payload.contentString: Hi Homer, your blood work just came back. Would you like to come in to talk about it?
Just tell me doc, I can't bear to wait any longer.
If you insist... Unfortunately, the results came back positive. You're allergic to peanuts.
Are either of available to take Homer's vital signs before his physical tomorrow?
I have the day off tomorrow, so I cannot.
I can do it, but it will have to be quick and he must be on time.
